1.00	The_Beach_(2000_film)	The Beach (film)	The Beach is a 2000 adventure drama film directed by Danny Boyle and based on the 1996 novel of the same name by Alex Garland, which was adapted for the film by John Hodge. The film stars Leonardo DiCaprio and features Tilda Swinton, Robert Carlyle, Virginie Ledoyen and Guillaume Canet. It was filmed on the Thai island Koh Phi Phi.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bc/The_Beach_film.jpg/220px-The_Beach_film.jpg
